{"tid":148190,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一條高斯定律問題","createTime":"2017-03-08T11:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T14:51:04.000Z","uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d67ec50d1068def7018a048ac3484e70498c53","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"Two uniformly charged, infinite, nonconducting planes are parallel to a yz plane and positioned<br />\nat x = &minus;50 cm and x + 50 cm. The charge densities on the planes are &minus;50nC/m2 and +25nC/m2<br />\n,<br />\nrespectively. What is the magnitude of the potential difference between the origin and the point<br />\non the x axis at x = +80 cm?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vm25Zrm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvm25Zrm.jpg&h=946ef176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解個2個 planes 既 charge densities &minus;50nC/m2 and +25nC/m2<br />\n係唔同既"},{"pid":"8d8702c6ec7130c2888b5a6bb64e1a09fa2679fa","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:08:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddfb27ade02ce20ee62b9dba5b89be6ae752dc94","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ed4068b9a7ca70fa47750d3b834aff968378433","tid":148190,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"同私有產權有關"},{"pid":"fab38dbe4f4fa433d9c8f4e78de7c377ec17c211","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同私有產權有關</blockquote><br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f239aa65e7069894fc03d56b94c1252599bbe1d9","tid":148190,"uid":79376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"charge densities 可以唔同，我地而家x=+50 同 x=-50 只係話左比我地聽兩個plane既位置，但冇講射e-field 果個野（origin？）既位置。所以兩個plane 同個origin(?) 既距離唔同，得到既charge density 都可以唔同。"},{"pid":"6e49e8aba46a784892e92cd581968df7a219f9d1","tid":148190,"uid":79376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>charge densities 可以唔同，我地而家x=+50 同 x=-50 只係話左比我地聽兩個plane既位置，但冇講射e-field 果個野（origin？）既位置。所以兩個plane 同個origin(?) 既距離唔同，得到既charge density 都可以唔同。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://physics.stackexchange.com/questions/283913/find-the-potential-between-two-non-conducting-parallel-planes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphysics.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F283913%2Ffind-the-potential-between-two-non-conducting-parallel-planes&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bceaf903\" target=\"_blank\">http://physics.stackexchange.com/questions/283913/find-the-potential-between-two-non-conducting-parallel-planes</a><br />\n跟著自己睇<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb884cefcf4133ae1892f333272b55f00bfa1bc","tid":148190,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbffde30ce58a6e863bf9d0e4af9f6271b682e0","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f627923aae6e057a84c4df0a913148f50ab7d50","tid":148190,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density唔一樣<br />\n咁個E就自然唔一樣<br />\n無話一定要一樣"},{"pid":"83f6f0e4713bd281c9325a5ee988fe31628bf3ad","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density唔一樣<br />\n咁個E就自然唔一樣<br />\n無話一定要一樣</blockquote><br />\n但個圓柱parallel 块平板<br />\nr又一樣<br />\n點解E會唔同"},{"pid":"fc078d92a9ebd0059e69dbe55d6ee38f8e5eefe4","tid":148190,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:24:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同私有產權有關</blockquote><br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEcon Coase Thm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7d7cd5836d41c77d2aa4a3fe2498f75bccaca7","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同私有產權有關</blockquote><br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEcon Coase Thm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心唔明"},{"pid":"699aaecf5f5c39fadc3b9b0c2cb5a53837f1e154","tid":148190,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density唔一樣<br />\n咁個E就自然唔一樣<br />\n無話一定要一樣</blockquote><br />\n但個圓柱parallel 块平板<br />\nr又一樣<br />\n點解E會唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density 都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65e2c05f52d437e47c6ea5a5a561fb56cc2412c","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density唔一樣<br />\n咁個E就自然唔一樣<br />\n無話一定要一樣</blockquote><br />\n但個圓柱parallel 块平板<br />\nr又一樣<br />\n點解E會唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density 都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係想知點解唔一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用E=q/4pie r^2&epsilon;0 計<br />\nr 同q相同 咁E咪一樣<br />\n再用E計返&sigma; 唔係一樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeb2c5954a734f89f59d31fc48a3a7d2a8be265","tid":148190,"uid":72445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同私有產權有關</blockquote><br />\n要問張五常"},{"pid":"6689ae79f28e8f2d7d6879ddf02712f167d95bf2","tid":148190,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density唔一樣<br />\n咁個E就自然唔一樣<br />\n無話一定要一樣</blockquote><br />\n但個圓柱parallel 块平板<br />\nr又一樣<br />\n點解E會唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density 都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係想知點解唔一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用E=q/4pie r^2&epsilon;0 計<br />\nr 同q相同 咁E咪一樣<br />\n再用E計返&sigma; 唔係一樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個electric field本身就係in 左係個plane上每一點一粒charge係r既結果<br />\n<br />\n因為呢個case係一個infinite plane<br />\n所以用symmetry argument就唔洗計<br />\n係E=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0"},{"pid":"e9edd68f03b1371c523a660a9be6d9c18e4b3692","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你想問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density唔一樣<br />\n咁個E就自然唔一樣<br />\n無話一定要一樣</blockquote><br />\n但個圓柱parallel 块平板<br />\nr又一樣<br />\n點解E會唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density 都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係想知點解唔一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用E=q/4pie r^2&epsilon;0 計<br />\nr 同q相同 咁E咪一樣<br />\n再用E計返&sigma; 唔係一樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個electric field本身就係in 左係個plane上每一點一粒charge係r既結果<br />\n<br />\n因為呢個case係一個infinite plane<br />\n所以用symmetry argument就唔洗計<br />\n係E=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0</blockquote><br />\n但想計net electric fields at the origin x=0<br />\n係咪E= &sigma;1&sigma;2/2&epsilon;0<br />\n就得"},{"pid":"70abd7a0ce7d6b73aa65d180784328fd47d75862","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]<br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既電場強度一樣<br />\nE=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0<br />\n咁點解&sigma;唔係相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density唔一樣<br />\n咁個E就自然唔一樣<br />\n無話一定要一樣</blockquote><br />\n但個圓柱parallel 块平板<br />\nr又一樣<br />\n點解E會唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density 都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係想知點解唔一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用E=q/4pie r^2&epsilon;0 計<br />\nr 同q相同 咁E咪一樣<br />\n再用E計返&sigma; 唔係一樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個electric field本身就係in 左係個plane上每一點一粒charge係r既結果<br />\n<br />\n因為呢個case係一個infinite plane<br />\n所以用symmetry argument就唔洗計<br />\n係E=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0</blockquote><br />\n但想計net electric fields at the origin x=0<br />\n係咪E= &sigma;1+&sigma;2/2&epsilon;0<br />\n就得"},{"pid":"fc78e715160d96d75c71388f3f91543925e508b3","tid":148190,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]<br />\n想個兩個planes既&sigma;點解唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個兩個planes既