c fields<br />\n點解係70-q1/2&epsilon;0<br />\n唔係&sigma;1+&sigma;2-70/2&epsilon;0"},{"pid":"82c52976f74b877b15f2b8e22d6c98f5f8628ea9","tid":148190,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n但個圓柱parallel 块平板<br />\nr又一樣<br />\n點解E會唔同</blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density 都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係想知點解唔一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用E=q/4pie r^2&epsilon;0 計<br />\nr 同q相同 咁E咪一樣<br />\n再用E計返&sigma; 唔係一樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個electric field本身就係in 左係個plane上每一點一粒charge係r既結果<br />\n<br />\n因為呢個case係一個infinite plane<br />\n所以用symmetry argument就唔洗計<br />\n係E=&sigma;/2&epsilon;0</blockquote><br />\n但想計net electric fields at the origin x=0<br />\n係咪E= &sigma;1+&sigma;2/2&epsilon;0<br />\n就得</blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n咁加個 point x=70 都係搵x=70 net electric fields<br />\n點解係70-q1/2&epsilon;0<br />\n唔係&sigma;1+&sigma;2-70/2&epsilon;0</blockquote><br />\n完全唔明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n<br />\nE=-(&sigma;1+&sigma;2)/2&epsilon;0 for x&lt;-50<br />\nE= (&sigma;1-&sigma;2)/2&epsilon;0 for -50&lt;x&lt;50<br />\nE= (&sigma;1+&sigma;2)/2&epsilon;0 for x&gt;50"},{"pid":"2b0594a7b4c6f66dad78a59959335b13bc49b48a","tid":148190,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咁個charge density 都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係想知點解唔一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用E=q/4pie r^2&epsilon;0 計<br />\nr 同q相同 咁E咪一樣<br />\n再用E計返&sigma; 唔係一樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor